		<title>What is Leverage in Crypto &#038; How Does It Work? (Guide)</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/what-is-leverage-in-crypto/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Staff Reporter]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 22:00:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Cryptocurrency]]></category>
